This paper is primarily focused on the design of a communication system for the tactile internet, which is a subfield of networked systems and the internet of things. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses the optimization of resource allocation, which falls under the category of information theory (cs.IT). The paper also deals with the issue of ensuring quality of service (QoS), which is a key concern in control systems (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of multiple antennas, which is a common technique in multimedia communication (cs.MM) and augmented reality (cs.AR).
